propClasses: Override or extend the styles applied to the component.
propIcon: The icon to display in the SpeedDial Floating Action Button.
propOpenIcon: The icon to display in the SpeedDial Floating Action Button when the SpeedDial is open.
stylesRoot: Styles applied to the root element.
stylesIcon: Styles applied to the icon component.
stylesIconOpen: Styles applied to the icon component if `open={true}`.
stylesIconWithOpenIconOpen: Styles applied to the icon when an `openIcon` is provided and if `open={true}`.
stylesOpenIcon: Styles applied to the `openIcon` if provided.
stylesOpenIconOpen: Styles applied to the `openIcon` if provided and if `open={true}`.
